This model is a general case of regulated systems. Classical heat transfers occur only through convection, conduction, radiation, or any combination of these.
Therefore, this model shows only the Heat flows from the Cooling/HeatingSystems to the Air inside the Room, and between the Air inside the Room and the environment.
